{
  "name": "重生坩堝 Cauldron of Rebirth",
  "type": "equipment",
  "img": "icons/containers/kitchenware/vase-clay-cracked-grey.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p class=\"WordSection1\"><em>奇物, 極珍稀（</em><span class=\"GramE\"><em>需德魯</em></span><em>伊或邪</em><span class=\"GramE\"><em>術師同調</em></span><em>）</em></p><p class=\"WordSection1\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">這隻微型小鍋的鑄鐵側邊上刻有英雄群像的浮雕。你可以將這件坩堝作為法器使用，且其可以作為</span><span class=\"bbccolor\"><em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.OA4mCsVxg6nUrLjV]{探知Scrying}</em></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">法術的代替材料。當你完成</span><span class=\"GramE\">一</span>次長休時，你可以使用坩堝製造一瓶<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.itempack.Item.8E52DDA51F06A5F3]{高等治療藥水Potion of Greater Healing}</em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">。藥水持續</span>24<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">個小時，若其沒有被使用，則它失去魔力。</span><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">作為一個動作，你可以讓坩堝增大至足以容納一個中型生物。你可以用一個動作讓坩堝恢復其普通大小，並且無害地將任何它無法容納的東西轉出到最近未被佔據的位置。</span><br /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">如果你將一個類人生物的屍體放入坩堝之中並將</span>200<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">磅的鹽（耗費</span>10<span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">金幣）</span><span class=\"GramE\">覆蓋</span>到坩堝之上持續八小時，那麼鹽會被消耗，而那個生物會在下一個黎明時復活，如同<em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e_classpack.new-icon.Item.63gAxMpLpbVW9Oja]{死者復活Raise dead}</em><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:11pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-ascii-font-family:Arial;mso-hansi-font-family:Arial\">法術。使用后七日之內，坩堝的此項屬性無法再次使用。</span><br /></p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
